title: Video: high school quarterback scores amazing touchdown
text:
Video Image High School Quarterback's dazzling touchdown 0:19 American Football: Take a look at this high school quarterback dazzles on his way to scoring an awesome touchdown
October 14th 2015 7 days ago /video/video.news.com.au/Sport/More Sports/ The young quarterback looks to be trapped but masterfully escapes five tackles on his way to a touchdown.
Olgun Uluc FOX SPORTS HIGH School quarterback Rene Ortega looks like a future star. Watch as the youngster looks trapped, but somehow escapes for an amazing touchdown.
As the starting quarterback for Los Fresnos High School, Ortega looks to be tackled for a loss, but somehow managed to escape five tackles on his way to a 16-yard touchdown that took an incredible 17 seconds.
Emulating Cleveland Browns quarterback Johnny Manziel with the dazzling play, Ortega ultimately led his team to a 39-14 win over Harlingen South.
